ext_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00564">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 16. 7. [1896]</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
